@gampix.api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5000

### Users Endpoints

# Get all users
GET {{gampix.api_HostAddress}}/api/users

### Create user
POST {{gampix.api_HostAddress}}/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "juan_perez",
  "email": "juan@example.com",
  "initialBalance": 1000
}

### Games Endpoints

# Get all games
GET {{gampix.api_HostAddress}}/api/games

### Create game
POST {{gampix.api_HostAddress}}/api/games
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Barcelona vs Real Madrid",
  "description": "Clásico español",
  "startDate": "2026-04-15T20:00:00Z",
  "endDate": "2026-04-15T22:00:00Z",
  "oddsWin": 1.5
}

### Bets Endpoints

# Get all bets
GET {{gampix.api_HostAddress}}/api/bets

### Create bet
POST {{gampix.api_HostAddress}}/api/bets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "game": "Barcelona vs Real Madrid",
  "stake": 100,
  "winAmount": 150
}

### Get RTP
GET {{gampix.api_HostAddress}}/api/bets/rtp

### Get bets by game name
GET {{gampix.api_HostAddress}}/api/bets/game/Barcelona%20vs%20Real%20Madrid
